                    <outline text="Abstract #slide ">
                        <outline text="We then use the unifying language of regular matrix pencil eigensystems, nonnegative matrix factorisations and weak and strong Perron-Frobenius conditions in order to characterise solutions of a range of linear optimisation problems and non-cooperative matrix games. #signpost"/>
