                    <outline text="GAME #wfe-ignore-item ">
                        <outline text="Section $\ref{vulnerability_section}$ presents three possible monitoring strategies for the utility company: to monitor the daily average of forecasting data, to inspect the daily shape of the aggregated forecast, and to inspect the individual forecast data with the same level of detail. "/>
